import { StyleSheet, Text, View, Button, TouchableOpacity,ScrollView ,  KeyboardAvoidingView } from 'react-native'
import React from 'react'
import Field from './Field'
import { useWindowDimensions } from 'react-native';
import Login from './Login';
import Home from './Home';

export default function Signup ({navigation}) {
  const { height, width } = useWindowDimensions();
  return (
    <View style={{alignItems: 'center', width: width, backgroundColor: '#FFF8DC'}}>
    <Text style={{fontSize: 64, fontWeight: 'bold', marginTop: 10}}>Signup</Text>
    <Text style={{fontSize: 18, fontWeight: 'bold', marginBottom: 30}}>Create a new account</Text>
    

    <View style={{ backgroundColor: '#FFFFFF',height: height, width: width, borderTopLeftRadius: 200, paddingTop: 100,alignItems: 'center'}}>
    {/* <ScrollView showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false} style={{flex:1}}>
        <KeyboardAvoidingView behavior='position'> */}
      <Field placeholder="Username" />
      <Field placeholder="Email" keyboardType={'email-address'}/>
      <Field placeholder="Password" secureTextEntry={true}/>
      {/* </KeyboardAvoidingView>
      </ScrollView> */}
      <View style={{display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'row',justifyContent: 'center', width: width}}>
        <Text style={{fontSize: 13, marginBottom: 10 }}>By signing in, you agree to our </Text>
        <Text style={{fontSize: 13, fontWeight: 'bold',  marginBottom: 10 }}>Terms and Conditions </Text>
      </View>
      <View  style={{width: 250}} >
      <Button title="Signup" color="#0000FF" onPress={()=>{navigation.navigate('Home')}} />
      </View>
      <View style={{display:'flex', flexDirection: 'row', justifyContent: 'center', marginTop: 20}}>
        <Text >Don't have an account ? </Text>
        <TouchableOpacity onPress={()=>{navigation.navigate('Login')}}>
          <Text  style={{fontWeight:'bold'}}>Login</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
      </View>
    </View>
  </View>
  )
}
